Pre-Game Insights: Thomas Partey, Joseph Paintsil, Kingsley Schindler, and Osman Ibrahim have pulled out and been ruled out of the 2025 TotalEnergies Africa Cup of Nations qualifiers against Sudan due to injuries.
The Black Stars are set to face Sudan on Thursday, October 10 and Tuesday, October 15, 2024 in two very important Africa Cup of Nations qualifiers.
